stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Attempt1: memory created
    Attempt1 --> Success: enrichment succeeds
    Attempt1 --> Attempt2: error (wait 5s)
    Attempt2 --> Success: enrichment succeeds
    Attempt2 --> Attempt3: error (wait 25s)
    Attempt3 --> Success: enrichment succeeds
    Attempt3 --> Failed: error (max attempts)
    Success --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]: log error, stop retrying
    
    note right of Attempt1
        attempt=0
        backoff=5s
    end note
    
    note right of Attempt2
        attempt=1
        backoff=5s * 5^1 = 25s
    end note
    
    note right of Attempt3
        attempt=2
        backoff=5s * 5^2 = 125s
        (max attempts reached)
    end note